  <dt id="1_01">
   What if I can't donate time or money now?
  </dt>
  <dd>
  <p>
  The <%= org_name %> pledge is designed so that you can spend the early years of
  your career building up your capacity to do good later. For example, if you
  started a company, you wouldn't be able to give much money at first, but you'd
  be able to give 10% of your lifetime income once you'd got your company
  established. Similarly, a young person getting started in politics or
  campaigning won't have much influence at first, but will be able to do a lot of
  good over their whole career.
  </p>
  <a href="#content">back to top</a>
  </dd>

  <dt id="1_02">
  How do I decide which causes to support?
  </dt>
