  Have a look at our blog post [Link to Sasha's blog post], which goes into
  more detail about this.
  </p>
  <a href="#content">back to top</a>
  </dd>

  <dt id="1_03">
  What do you mean by 10% of time?
  </dt>
  <dd>
  <p>
  At least 10% of your time at work, so that would be 4 hours of a 40 hour
  week. However, for many researchers and influencers, there will not be a
  strict separation between the time they spend helping and the rest of their
  work.
  </p>
